# GRAPHICS::GET_CURRENT_NUMBER_OF_CLOUD_PHOTOS

## Summary
Returns the current number of photos on the cloud. You can only call this after GET_STATUS_OF_SORTED_LIST_OPERATION has returned PHOTO_OPERATION_SUCCEEDED

## Returns
* **INT**
